[Meeting Announcement and Call for Participation
Modeling the Spread and Control of Ebola in W. Africa
-----------------------------------------------------
Historic Academy of Medicine at Georgia Tech, Atlanta, Georgia, USA, 22-23 Jan 2015

This meeting will highlight concepts, challenges, and results arising from the use of models to predict the spread and facilitate the control of Ebola in W. Africa. For more information, go to http://bioinformatics.gatech.edu/ebola-modeling-workshop or email: <ebola-modeling-workshop@gatech.edu>.

I am continually amazed at the number of people who continue to model Ebola based on what are acknowledged to be grossly misleading statistics. But perhaps that means I need to attend the conference. - Mod.JW

